dBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T07:33:24.000Z","msg":"唉 香港人就係咁<br />\n憎人富貴厭人貧<br />\n佢雖然冇後顧之憂<br />\n但佢真係好有勇氣<br />\n唔係個個都敢讀完書由零開始做一樣嘢<br />\n你估學一門新嘢仲要去到攞國際獎容易?<br />\n你估真係比d錢 死磨爛磨就做到?<br />\n見到呢班on9就知佢地心理扭曲到咩地步<br />\n真係可悲"},{"pid":"da4e571a2f534aa80e924a504f9e19ce38512df1","tid":347514,"uid":26708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T07:35:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都想出生於小康之家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aefa080876ac0602a9e78a9e9843d6a6164d3d89","tid":347514,"uid":9436,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T07:42:55.000Z","msg":"平時又屌人窮人唔好生仔<br />\n而家人哋小康出身叻仔又屌人屋企有個錢先可以追夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f803bdd887e5f6c73597d111c30d30ac0e1d395","tid":347514,"uid":69037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T07:46:51.000Z","msg":"就算比你係佢<br />\n你都冇佢咁嘅勇氣啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f194c2470c733f742f478335b28a8c9f91c4335","tid":347514,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T07:49:20.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"e49bc4b8d5cdedf92a14353a35497046147ec654","tid":347514,"uid":58645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T08:05:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個仔做醫生律師，每次老母間談話都可以引來羡慕<br />\n一個爛鳩獎最多俾老母威一年半年，下次老母都唔好意思話自己個仔係拿左個乜乜乜獎<br />\n<br />\n&quot;吓？乜獎黎嫁？未聽過既？&quot; &quot;吓？兩年前攞獎？\t 咁今年冇參加嗱？&quot;</blockquote><br />\n22年前，有個後生仔喺英國讀緊建，最後因。為鍾意唱歌，放棄左學業，毅然返香港參加歌唱比賽"},{"pid":"b5a121f667cd07e280bac0e136306cb9c37ff128","tid":347514,"uid":91648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T09:46:52.000Z","msg":"邊度係尖子?"},{"pid":"bddf2648507084ff9d7cfd09e6b34dd96fa18d9c","tid":347514,"uid":9483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T10:14:53.000Z","msg":"有夢真好<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d592b125b07b075c029e6efa005a52c3cd401e16","tid":347514,"uid":35430,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T10:17:30.000Z","msg":"音樂 遊戲 藝術<br />\n係作為人類身份嘅證明"},{"pid":"f64cbe9a0ff14f7cb3723a8c8e0bc2d9f5cd3db9","tid":347514,"uid":23988,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T10:23:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>根本上面留comment話小康之家 乜乜柒柒果啲 <br />\n比你真係有錢 係咪真係有信心做到事主咁先 事主份決心同勤力 我覺得真係值得欣賞</blockquote><br />\n認同。唔覺得連登仔會有毅力追夢"},{"pid":"f061024205c4d0c7390d971b88fda7a7746aabd0","tid":347514,"uid":70028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T10:30:50.000Z","msg":"香港人識唔識欣賞人？"},{"pid":"861b582525b2528cc6314a048643e940d0084261","tid":347514,"uid":2544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T10:33:33.000Z","msg":"現實屋企有錢先有機會<br />\n但都好欣賞佢做的野<br />\n<br />\n最後想講<br />\n點解個個報導追夢的新聞都無人大方咁講自己屋企有錢 一尾講自己點努力之類<br />\n大方啲 唔好咁虛榮心 未仲有感染力"},{"pid":"d20a70976f4d8a20ac3b4c05c9de8bd8c9b27278","tid":347514,"uid":53062,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T10:56:19.000Z","msg":"冇否定佢的努力同才華<br />\n不過有錢先有資格追夢<br />\n俾著窮撚細路唔返工讀音樂，父母一巴打撚死佢"},{"pid":"cfdba763010084e82a5a32b9aedfe5a5e7eba575","tid":347514,"uid":79471,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T10:58:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>冇否定佢的努力同才華<br />\n不過有錢先有資格追夢<br />\n俾著窮撚細路唔返工讀音樂，父母一巴打撚死佢</blockquote><br />\n冇人叫你理你老豆老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13c53850edc7e5386d93ebcf08e3abc4b115eb39","tid":347514,"uid":53062,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T11:01:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>冇否定佢的努力同才華<br />\n不過有錢先有資格追夢<br />\n俾著窮撚細路唔返工讀音樂，父母一巴打撚死佢</blockquote><br />\n冇人叫你理你老豆老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n窮人細細個已經俾父母灌輸養兒防老觀念<img src=\"/assets/fa