480fd7a9cb052","tid":347514,"uid":17008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T11:06:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>替港？至撚憎平時就理撚你死，一出名就死癡爛癡替乜爭光咁。人地靠自己拎個獎關人撚事咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n正想咁講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n同意，有得簡都唔想香港抽水<br />\n失敗就諗野有問題有病唔實際天真樂觀<br />\n成功就叻仔兩個字"},{"pid":"21c154c68a8cb10125a82e9633dfa5bde7756f81","tid":347514,"uid":17008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T11:07:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>替港？至撚憎平時就理撚你死，一出名就死癡爛癡替乜爭光咁。人地靠自己拎個獎關人撚事咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n莫講話無鼓勵，直情係打壓"},{"pid":"9e6e30804ecd3cd24da78a6f9c53d69112b66e3c","tid":347514,"uid":8858,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T11:11:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>替港？至撚憎平時就理撚你死，一出名就死癡爛癡替乜爭光咁。人地靠自己拎個獎關人撚事咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n莫講話無鼓勵，直情係打壓</blockquote><br />\n講得啱呀，係打壓多過推動<br />\n係個人嘅光榮唔係替港爭光，真係關港撚事"},{"pid":"97b1047af77ea769e8fc3cf344c59fd8a3d205a1","tid":347514,"uid":49456,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T11:11:09.000Z","msg":"Austin慶幸生於小康之家，可以放心追夢，<br />\n<br />\n係事實<br />\n<br />\n但捱到28歲都唔易啦<br />\n每年過時過節，見到隔離鄰舍都抽下你水<br />\n<br />\n可能小康會wfc啩，我用左窮人思維諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當24歲Grad，四年都追夢無正職所承受既壓力好大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4a70fad2170caa17737ce64a99d69da4716bb14","tid":347514,"uid":2295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T11:11:35.000Z","msg":"香港唔似外國有社會保障<br />\n要靠自己 搵唔到錢<br />\n老左拎老綜真係同乞食無咩分別<br />\n唔好成日講咩價值觀<br />\n個社會造就出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f432a856af3144d3187d3c57e7cc0d54d7fab4eb","tid":347514,"uid":113675,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T11:34:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港唔似外國有社會保障<br />\n要靠自己 搵唔到錢<br />\n老左拎老綜真係同乞食無咩分別<br />\n唔好成日講咩價值觀<br />\n個社會造就出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n垃圾政府造就出黎"},{"pid":"9dbae22c5364f2ae0bf04de5944191f8cb2c04ea","tid":347514,"uid":35221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T11:50:24.000Z","msg":"千祈唔好返黎香港，留係英國，放眼世界<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"209e103acb59fd8693263ce0a5be7e0820668341","tid":347514,"uid":17008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T12:04:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>香港唔似外國有社會保障<br />\n要靠自己 搵唔到錢<br />\n老左拎老綜真係同乞食無咩分別<br />\n唔好成日講咩價值觀<br />\n個社會造就出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n垃圾政府造就出黎</blockquote><br />\n對<br />\n七百萬港人換曬做英國人<br />\n一樣會變成咁<br />\n所以唔支持無乜好講<br />\n畢竟個人選擇，佢明明唔係食老綜又有工作又有犧牲又承受風險，但世上的確有部分人係會以攻擊性既目光睇逐夢既人，果堆人確實有待進步"},{"pid":"34dac3783fcf3b803126a0ad02f8ab4464d72f19","tid":347514,"uid":43372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T12:22:18.000Z","msg":"替乜撚野<br />\n關你香港撚事咩<br />\n人地做果陣又冇支持過出過力<br />\n有咩成就就同香港掛勾攞彩<br />\n真係好撚噁心"},{"pid":"1fc13e396ef2670bf6e83b5ff687c0aa7f549053","tid":347514,"uid":43372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T12:23:14.000Z","msg":"替乜撚野<br />\n關你香港撚事咩<br />\n人地做果陣又冇支持過出過力<br />\n有咩成就就同香港掛勾攞彩<br />\n真係好撚噁心"},{"pid":"261de44d1accf8f96ccec58c88f02a6eb756e374","tid":347514,"uid":126247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T12:58:06.000Z","msg":"香港真係好多垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06ea954dcd16aa58f22a38965f0302d22519ed1f","tid":347514,"uid":126247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T13:00:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港唔似外國有社會保障<br />\n要靠自己 搵唔到錢<br />\n老左拎老綜